Usage: (COMMAND ... | [--project PROJECT] [--as PROFILE] [--rebar] [--idle-timeout SECONDS])

Available options:
        --project <PROJECT>  Path to directory with project, or to a JSON file (defaults to `.`)
        --as <PROFILE>  Rebar3 profile to pickup (default is test)
        --rebar         Run with rebar
        --idle-timeout <SECONDS>  Idle timeout in seconds before auto-shutdown (default: 1800,
                        0=never)
    -h, --help          Prints help information

Available commands:
    stop    Stop all running daemons
    status  Show daemon status for this project
